  <data name="announcementLabel.Text"><value>Windows Admin Center brings together new and familiar features in one browser-based app. It runs on a server or a PC, and there’s no additional cost beyond your Windows licenses. For hyper-converged clusters, you get a unified view of VMs, storage, and networking, cluster-wide monitoring, and simpler management of volumes and VMs.​</value></data>
